Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.94,0:00:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然被赋予死神的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.13,0:00:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.04,0:00:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的世界就改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.05,0:00:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神代行黑崎一护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.01,0:00:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护重要的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.97,0:00:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深沉的信念爆发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.01,0:00:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挥动起灵魂之刃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.06,0:02:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是...双殛之丘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.81,0:02:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎你 阿散井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.22,0:02:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝染队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.35,0:02:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.03,0:02:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这...到底是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.12,0:02:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下朽木露琪亚 你退下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.24,0:02:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝染队长 为什么你还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.15,0:02:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...与其说这个...为什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.17,0:02:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.73,0:02:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不可能没听到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.08,0:02:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说让你放下朽木露琪亚 退到一边去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.12,0:02:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿散井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.14,0:02:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南之心脏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.28,0:02:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北之瞳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.39,0:02:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西之指尖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.42,0:02:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东之脚跟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.72,0:02:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集聚风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.05,0:03:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挥洒雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.66,0:03:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缚道之五十八
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.46,0:03:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掴趾追雀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.40,0:03:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,31
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.74,0:03:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,64
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.27,0:03:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,83
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.71,0:03:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,97
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.24,0:03:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转移地点找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东 332
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北 1566
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.56,0:03:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是双殛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.55,0:03:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.59,0:03:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 请尽快搜索并确认\N所有队长和副队长的位置 并转告他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.73,0:03:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所知道的\N关于蓝染惣右介的一切事情 以及他的行踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.66,0:03:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再把这消息也转告给那些旅祸们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.51,0:03:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.11,0:03:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.77,0:03:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在要去救日番谷队长和雏森副队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.90,0:04:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑白之罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.78,0:04:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二十二之桥梁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.25,0:04:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六十六之冠带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.38,0:04:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足迹 远雷 尖峰 回地 夜伏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.50,0:04:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云海 苍之队列
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.76,0:04:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满贯太元顶天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缚道之七十七
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.94,0:04:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天挺 空罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.51,0:04:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕捉...成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.60,0:04:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位护廷十三队队长 副队长 以及副队长代理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.92,0:04:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有各位旅祸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.11,0:04:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是四番队副队长虎徹勇音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.99,0:04:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.12,0:04:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常紧急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.60,0:04:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是来自四番队队长\N卯之花烈以及我虎徹勇音的紧急传信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托请暂时仔细听我说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.12,0:04:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我要说的全都是真实的状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.39,0:04:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.64,0:04:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝染他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.98,0:04:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.96,0:05:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么办 山爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.28,0:05:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是做这种事的时候...不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.93,0:05:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长他...竟然输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.87,0:05:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说对雏森...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.78,0:05:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会做什么的吗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.77,0:05:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四十六室...竟然被全灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.89,0:05:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长他...竟然是个叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.77,0:05:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东仙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.91,0:05:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您听到了吗 茧利大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.76,0:05:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 听到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.42,0:05:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您打算怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.83,0:05:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 没什么兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.11,0:05:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的那个 是真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.31,0:05:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 但也有可能是敌人的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.09,0:05:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 应该是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.01,0:06:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道没感觉到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从顶上传来的灵压
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.85,0:06:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露琪亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.07,0:06:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.87,0:06:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 我拒绝 蓝染队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.93,0:06:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.76,0:06:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 银
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.05,0:06:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是顽固啊 阿散井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.90,0:06:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要你把朽木露琪亚放下并退开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.25,0:06:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不答应就没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.76,0:06:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就成全你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.26,0:06:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就这么抱着朽木露琪亚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.92,0:06:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要把你的手臂也一起留下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.21,0:07:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.72,0:07:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.74,0:07:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你闪躲得很好嘛 阿散井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.04,0:07:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你成长了啊 我很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.74,0:07:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果可以 我还是希望你不要太坚持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.10,0:07:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要想在不踩死蚂蚁的前提下 踩着它走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那力道是很难拿捏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.82,0:07:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我作为你的前任长官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.40,0:07:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不忍心看着你死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.87,0:07:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.77,0:07:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别说话 露琪亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.86,0:07:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么不忍心看着我死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.11,0:07:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你为什么要杀死雏森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.24,0:07:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她没有我就活不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这样教导她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.01,0:08:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得我杀了她是对她的同情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.26,0:08:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不愿意亲手杀她 这也是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.61,0:08:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我费了点心思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.72,0:08:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让她和吉良 日番谷他们互相残杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是进展得不太顺利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.01,0:08:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.97,0:08:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我亲自动手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.17,0:08:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.54,0:08:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说吉良也好 雏森也罢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.95,0:08:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都被你玩弄于股掌之中咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一样啊 阿散井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.66,0:08:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.08,0:08:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经不是我所熟知的蓝染队长了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.29,0:08:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你究竟是出于什么目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.08,0:08:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就算是死 我也不会把露琪亚交给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.43,0:08:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不是你所熟知的蓝染惣右介了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.49,0:08:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗憾的是 那是你的错觉 阿散井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.33,0:09:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所熟知的蓝染惣右介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.20,0:09:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始就并不存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.92,0:09:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咆哮吧 蛇尾丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.40,0:09:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,始解吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.63,0:09:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭你现在这一身的伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.27,0:09:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连多争取点时间都做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.68,0:09:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个让人伤脑筋的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.93,0:09:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然赤手...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在那三人当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是最麻烦的一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.54,0:09:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿散井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.31,0:09:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾确信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.84,0:09:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当初遇到你们三人的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.77,0:10:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就确信你们三人可以利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.89,0:10:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此当你们三人加入护廷十三队的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.40,0:10:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就马上安排你们进了五番队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.44,0:10:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后将相对来说\N更能派上用场的两人安排为我和银的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.21,0:10:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于最麻烦的你 我很快就派去了其他队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.27,0:10:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我的直觉是正确的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.97,0:10:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最后再说一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.86,0:10:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下朽木露琪亚 退到一边去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.89,0:10:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等...等一下 蓝染队长 我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.83,0:10:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.97,0:10:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.90,0:10:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋...次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.57,0:10:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.12,0:10:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁说...我要放手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.99,0:10:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.01,0:10:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是遗憾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.17,0:11:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.09,0:11:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干吗 蹲在那里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.26,0:11:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像露琪亚很重一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.29,0:11:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.66,0:11:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.79,0:11:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一护...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.75,0:11:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.49,0:11:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.40,0:11:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要你来帮忙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.75,0:11:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.23,0:12:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是让你带个露琪亚 你就搞得这么狼狈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.09,0:12:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只是逃走而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.81,0:12:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带个行李对你来说也还是太重了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.65,0:12:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.98,0:12:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你自己才是糟糕透顶呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.63,0:12:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.90,0:12:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是对来救你的人该说的话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.63,0:12:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.64,0:12:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来是想跟你说谢谢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.46,0:12:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.29,0:12:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要我挑战闭气的新纪录吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在讲话的时候那么重地把我压在胸前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.78,0:12:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.05,0:12:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我随便出手不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.89,0:12:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以没阻止他中途冲了进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.45,0:12:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.27,0:12:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要清除的灰尘不管是一粒还是两粒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来也都是一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙就是...蓝染吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.98,0:12:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.80,0:12:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有逃走的力气吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.47,0:13:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有 但我还是要留下来战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.81,0:13:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该也明白的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算能逃走也是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.69,0:13:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 虽然不能说能打败他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但至少也要尽可能牵制住他们的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.15,0:13:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堂堂正正地从这里下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 真拿你没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.62,0:13:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 我们就暂时站在同一战线上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.74,0:13:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这招我只能用一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.54,0:13:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果打中的话 敌人一定会露出破绽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.24,0:13:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要把握住机会攻击这个破绽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.43,0:13:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.32,0:13:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会有些痛哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.94,0:13:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍耐一下 蛇尾丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.98,0:13:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 蛇尾丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.39,0:13:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狒牙决咬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.74,0:14:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.65,0:14:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本打算将你拦腰砍断的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.10,0:14:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砍得太浅了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.61,0:14:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎...怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.42,0:14:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.26,0:14:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.37,0:15:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可...恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.88,0:15:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.68,0:15:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.83,0:15:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体...动不了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.16,0:15:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木露琪亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.13,0:15:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.43,0:15:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你因为受到我的灵压的影响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以身体无法动弹了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.47,0:15:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.64,0:15:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.79,0:15:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有意识啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.08,0:16:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远在你实力之上的生命力 反而伤害了你自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.76,0:16:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好还是不要动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.96,0:16:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们已经发挥了你们的作用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.87,0:16:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的使命已经结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.31,0:16:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.50,0:16:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.80,0:16:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就知道你们要从西流魂街入侵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.14,0:16:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我早就在那附近布置了眼线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.92,0:16:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一旦发生什么情况 就让银直接过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.36,0:16:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对人手进行了暗中调配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.32,0:16:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下瀞灵壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.09,0:16:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并在门内安排队长级别的人手巡逻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.08,0:16:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.41,0:16:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入侵的方法就只剩下志波空鹤的花鹤大炮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.81,0:16:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是华丽的入侵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.62,0:16:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这些入侵者是\N能从队长级别的人手中脱逃掉的实力派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.80,0:17:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这势必会使瀞灵廷内\N死神们的注意力被那边吸引过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.48,0:17:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实在的 你们进入廷内以后的表现真是可圈可点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.29,0:17:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托你们的福 就算是有一名队长被杀也没造成太大的骚动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.04,0:17:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就让我的行动方便了许多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.08,0:17:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等...等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.28,0:17:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.45,0:17:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会知道我们会从西流魂街进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.03,0:17:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问得还真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用问吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.73,0:17:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西流魂街是浦原喜助的据点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.35,0:17:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所做的穿界门能侵入到的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.40,0:17:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只能是西流魂街了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.57,0:17:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 你那表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.21,0:17:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不是他的部下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.10,0:17:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不是受了浦原喜助的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.56,0:17:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而来夺回朽木露琪亚的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.35,0:17:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.15,0:17:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.78,0:18:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你们什么都不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.77,0:18:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.50,0:18:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.45,0:18:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来告诉你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.70,0:18:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神有最基本的四种战斗方式 你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.48,0:18:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斩术 白打 步法 鬼道这四种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.03,0:18:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这四种都是有所谓的强度界限存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.69,0:18:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是哪种能力只要练到极致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.68,0:18:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会碰上魂魄的强度之壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.09,0:18:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而停止成长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.70,0:18:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 那就是死神的极限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.36,0:18:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道没有突破它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.49,0:18:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将所有能力强化到超越极限的方法了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.42,0:18:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.88,0:18:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.14,0:18:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.64,0:18:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将死神"虚化"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.92,0:19:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神的"虚化" "虚"的"死神化"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.24,0:19:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能在这两个相反存在的境界中取得平衡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.82,0:19:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就能超越界限 使各种能力更加精进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.79,0:19:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这理论从很久以前开始就存在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.97,0:19:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 我也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.96,0:19:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗地里对"虚"进行了各种各样死神化的实验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.61,0:19:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能将自身灵压隐藏起来的"虚"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.32,0:19:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是碰触到 就能使斩魄刀消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.36,0:19:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并能与死神相融合的"虚"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.44,0:19:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不论是哪个\N都不如我期待的那样进展顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.93,0:19:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我以外还有其他的人也进行了研究
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.53,0:19:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有一个能找出这个方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.62,0:19:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是浦原喜助却创造出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.14,0:19:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能在瞬间超越"虚"与死神的界限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.39,0:19:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越尸魂界常识的物质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.95,0:20:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它名叫"崩玉"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.06,0:20:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是极其危险的物质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.92,0:20:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也这么感觉到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.16,0:20:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是他试图将"崩玉"破坏掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.20,0:20:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.97,0:20:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他竟然无法毁掉自己制造出来的"崩玉"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.12,0:20:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是他迫于无奈而使用了一个方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.77,0:20:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是在"崩玉"外设上防护壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.67,0:20:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并将其埋入其他魂魄里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.56,0:20:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该明白了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.11,0:20:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候 他藏"崩玉"的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.35,0:20:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你的体内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.04,0:20:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木露琪亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.22,0:20:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什...么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.78,0:20:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是当我知道这个消息的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.86,0:20:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你却已经在现世行踪不明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.28,0:20:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我直觉地感觉到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.27,0:20:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是浦原喜助耍了花样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.41,0:21:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他曾经开发了不含灵子的灵子体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.26,0:21:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用它制作了无法捕捉的义骸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.14,0:21:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此被尸魂界流放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.66,0:21:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入了义骸的死神就行踪不明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.32,0:21:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外 我想不出其他解释
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.30,0:21:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他被流放的理由还有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.93,0:21:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是进入义骸的死神的灵力会被持续分解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.79,0:21:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 进入里面的\N死神的灵力到何时也无法恢复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.86,0:21:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与义骸的联络变得迟钝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.05,0:21:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终使魂魄的灵力完全丧失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.92,0:21:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从死神转变为一般人类的魂魄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.78,0:21:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.10,0:21:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他并不是为了助你一臂之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.14,0:21:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是想让你变成人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.50,0:21:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使"崩玉"的所在被完全的隐藏起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.33,0:21:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
